The paper deals with the problem of face video retrieval using hashing techniques and deep learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves modeling techniques and optimization methods, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of deep learning and optimization methods suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper involves information retrieval techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the use of kernel mapping and structured matrix backpropagation suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
